Package cs.eng1.piazzapanic.food.interfaces

Interface Grillable

All Superinterfaces:
Holdable
All Known Implementing Classes:
BasicGrillable, Patty
public interface Grillable extends Holdable
A Holdable that can be grilled on GrillingStation Ingredients that implement this must have 2-step processing logic.
Author:
Andrey Samoilov, Ross Holmes
